<body><h1>Timesheet</h1>
<br><ul><li>Since Bugclipse helps track time spent on various tasks, it
is useful to report on the total time spent in a period in the form of
a timesheet<br></li><li>Select any FogBugz query/task and select
Timesheet from the context menu. The menu also provides various options
for the format of the report<br></li><li>The timesheet lists every
interval tracked in the repository within the given date range and sums
up the total work in the last row</li></ul><p></p>
